data.description: This home was completely remodeled in 2019. HOA Free!  Furnace, hot water heater, Air conditioner, and all appliances are all within 5 years old. New paint and energy efficient windows upstairs were installed 2023. The downstairs Family room is currently being used as a 4th bedroom. This can be a versatile bonus room. This home will wow you with the updates and the backyard was landscaped beautifully in 2022. The Gazebo is bolted to the concrete for summer shade while relaxing in the beautiful oasis. Full Irrigation with sprinkler system in the back, Xeriscape in front. This quiet neighborhood is perfect for any Owner. RV Parking with access gates to the Backyard. Plenty of room for all the toys or further landscaping. You don't want to miss this one.
